{"tid":1918691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓首爾一間保險公司至少64名員工及家屬確診","createTime":"2020-03-10T09:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T09:54:23.000Z","uid":41818,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"11321c9892237ceba7a876ebeedb712a57dee01c","tid":1918691,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"南韓首爾一間保險公司的客戶服務中心，爆發集體感染，至少64名中心職員及其家屬感染新型肺炎。市長形容，是首都圈地區最大規模集體感染事件。<br />\n<br />\n報道指涉事中心有大約200名員工，由於業務特殊，員工上班都不戴口罩。其中一名56歲女員工星期日首先確診，當局正為所有員工進行病毒檢測，相信確診病例會再增加。<br />\n<br />\n涉事中心位於一幢「商住兩用」大廈的11樓，當局對整棟大廈進行消毒，下令封鎖大廈1至12樓的商舖與辦公室，並要求13至19層住宅的住客自我家居隔離。\t\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513565-20200310.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513565-20200310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eShPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=e62a1a84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513565-20200310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=363be72c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513565-20200310.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1044420ee723615c5e0929c08cf5579fb754f1cd","tid":1918691,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:12:23.000Z","msg":"新感染群組"},{"pid":"439628f8996482ee6f4750278bbd627811235157","tid":1918691,"uid":49643,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"有人仲話武漢肺炎好似流感一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95c49d62dc4ebb67876f0c71ccb0fad67a5dace","tid":1918691,"uid":48458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11321c9892237ceba7a876ebeedb712a57dee01c","tid":1918691,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"南韓首爾一間保險公司的客戶服務中心，爆發集體感染，至少64名中心職員及其家屬感染新型肺炎。市長形容，是首都圈地區最大規模集體感染事件。<br />\n<br />\n報道指涉事中心有大約200名員工，由於業務特殊，員工上班都不戴口罩。其中一名56歲女員工星期日首先確診，當局正為所有員工進行病毒檢測，相信確診病例會再增加。<br />\n<br />\n涉事中心位於一幢「商住兩用」大廈的11樓，當局對整棟大廈進行消毒，下令封鎖大廈1至12樓的商舖與辦公室，並要求13至19層住宅的住客自我家居隔離。\t\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513565-20200310.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513565-20200310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eShPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=e62a1a84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513565-20200310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=363be72c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513565-20200310.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"&gt;由於業務特殊，員工上班都不戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n保險有乜特殊?<br />\n做G跑數?"},{"pid":"197e5d4522a1c9ff8c15599583a55a8819dfb35e","tid":1918691,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95c49d62dc4ebb67876f0c71ccb0fad67a5dace","tid":1918691,"uid":48458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11321c9892237ceba7a876ebeedb712a57dee01c","tid":1918691,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"南韓首爾一間保險公司的客戶服務中心，爆發集體感染，至少64名中心職員及其家屬感染新型肺炎。市長形容，是首都圈地區最大規模集體感染事件。<br />\n<br />\n報道指涉事中心有大約200名員工，由於業務特殊，員工上班都不戴口罩。其中一名56歲女員工星期日首先確診，當局正為所有員工進行病毒檢測，相信確診病例會再增加。<br />\n<br />\n涉事中心位於一幢「商住兩用」大廈的11樓，當局對整棟大廈進行消毒，下令封鎖大廈1至12樓的商舖與辦公室，並要求13至19層住宅的住客自我家居隔離。\t\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513565-20200310.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513565-20200310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eShPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=e62a1a84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%